CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper October 11, 1958, pg. 6, reads: "Public Health Nurses - Among the 21 recent appointments to districts of the Allegheny County Health Department are, left to right: Public Health Nurses Martha Hunt of 700 N. Highland Ave., Joanne H. Powell of 5320 Camp St., Viola E. Brown, of 3921 Menlo St., and LaFronza Flanagan of 533 Brushton ave. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Allegheny County Health Department public health nurses Martha Hunt, Joanne H. Powell, Viola E. Brown, and LaFronza Flanagan posed around table
